<h3>Apacheta¬†Ritual</h3>
An apacheta is a sacred stone cairn and acts like an acupuncture needle on Mother Earth‚Äôs Energy or nervous system called a Seque System.

Pachakuti Mesa Tradition (PMT) Carriers, Awahoo and Justine, describe how to build a an apacheta in the video below.

