<h4><img class="alignleft wp-image-7811" src="http://heartofthehealer.org/wp-content/uploads/teachers/0216..Garry_.sm_.jpg" alt="0216..Garry_.sm_" width="146" height="142" />Garry Caudill, CO</h4>
